        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/_scene_octopus.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 8de9aa5e-6d61-442f-a4c0-e5bba91cd3cd).Image",
        "Description": "Chuckles was living a good and funny life at the circus with his wife Claudia, and for a moment they were happy. That is until Chuckles found a vibrating bananna fish sex toy in Claudias purse on her way to work. It was at that moment chuckles knew she was having an affair at work, with who you might ask? He didn&apos;t know, but what he did know is that they would pay!\rRules: 1- claudia must be killed by picking up the rubber duck explosive and it must be detonated when near a group of people.",
